                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">P≈ôipojte se k na≈°√≠ komunitƒõ a z≈Østa≈àte v obraze s nejnovƒõj≈°√≠mi hern√≠mi zpr√°vami.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 mt-8 pt-8 text-center">
                <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">¬© 2024 Complay. V≈°echna pr√°va vyhrazena.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <!-- Analytics -->
